Package main.core.floorsubsystem

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    FloorListener
    This interface provides a generalization for FloorSubsystem views.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    EventObj
    This class provides an implementation of an object meant for storing the details of Elevator system-related events.
    Floor
    This class provides an implementation for the Floors in the FloorSubsystem.
    FloorController
    This class implements controller for the passing of information between a floor model and the floor view.
    FloorFrame
    This class implements a user interface for floor-related information.
    FloorPanel
    This class is an implementation of a component that displays the lights for a floor.
    FloorSubsystem
    This class provides an implementation for the Floor subsystem.
